window.addEventListener('scroll', unmissableOnScroll);
function unmissableOnScroll() {
var yOffset = window.pageYOffset;
var topDiv = document.getElementById("ad-unit-unmissable-top-sticky-banner");
if(topDiv && yOffset > 900){
var position = 0 - (yOffset-900);
if(position < -50){
closeUnmissable(true);
window.scrollBy(0, -50);
}
}
};
const unmissableCookieName = "unmissableIsClosed";
var isUnmissable = false;

function () {

});
}

function () {
$(this).removeClass(className);
});
}

removeClass(".has-mega-nav.unmissable", "unmissable");
}
});
window.googletag.pubads().addEventListener('slotRenderEnded',
function (event) {

});
}
});
function closeUnmissable(autoClosed) {
removeClass(".has-mega-nav", "unmissable");

removeClass(".compare-panel.close-panel", "unmissable");
removeClass(".site-nav-wrapper.csn-theme", "unmissable");

(function ClickTracker() {
var ignoreForLowerCaseList = ['data-webm-recommendationid', 'data-webm-slotid'];
var methods =
{
isValueValid : function(value){
return (typeof (value) !== 'undefined') && (value !== null);
},
tryGetAttributeValue: function(domElement, key)
{
var attributeValue = domElement.getAttribute(key);
var isKeyInIgnoreList = methods.isValueInArray(ignoreForLowerCaseList, key);
if (methods.isValueValid(attributeValue) && !isKeyInIgnoreList)
attributeValue = attributeValue.toLowerCase();
return attributeValue;
},

}

(function() {
function CsnInsightsHelper() {
var methods = {
setSessionCookie: function(cname, cvalue) {
document.cookie = cname + '=' + cvalue + ';path=/';
},
setCookie: function(cname, cvalue, exdays) {
var d = new Date();
d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
var expires = 'expires = ' + d.toUTCString();
document.cookie = cname + '=' + cvalue + ';' + expires + ';path=/';
},
getCookieValue: function(cname) {
var cookiesString = document.cookie || '';
var cookiesArr = cookiesString.split('; ');
for (var i = 0; i < cookiesArr.length; i++) {
var cookieStr = cookiesArr[i];
var index = cookieStr.indexOf('=');
if (index < 1) {
return undefined;
}
var cookieName = decodeURIComponent(cookieStr.substr(0, index));
if (cookieName === cname) {
return decodeURIComponent(cookieStr.substr(index + 1));
}
}
return undefined;
},
calculateScrollPercent: function(absScrollPercent) {
var scrollPercentCategory = 0;
if (absScrollPercent >= 25 && absScrollPercent <= 50)
scrollPercentCategory = 25;
else if (absScrollPercent >= 50 && absScrollPercent <= 75)
scrollPercentCategory = 50;
else if (absScrollPercent >= 75 && absScrollPercent < 99)
scrollPercentCategory = 75;
else if (absScrollPercent >= 99)
scrollPercentCategory = 100;
return scrollPercentCategory;
},
getScrollText: function(absScrollPercent) {
var scrolltext = "Less than 25%";
if (absScrollPercent == 100)
scrolltext = "Viewed 100 %";
else if (absScrollPercent >= 25)
scrolltext = "Viewed more than Or equal to" + absScrollPercent + " %";
return scrolltext;
},
isIPad: function (fieldsObject) {
const uAgent = window.navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();
const isIPad = (uAgent.indexOf('ipad') > -1 || uAgent.indexOf('mac') > -1) &&
window.navigator.maxTouchPoints && window.navigator.maxTouchPoints > 0 &&
'ontouchend' in document;
if (isIPad === true) {
/* convert json string to object and add a new key/value then convert it back to json string*/
var cd11 = JSON.parse(fieldsObject['dimension11']);
cd11['isipad'] = true;
fieldsObject['dimension11'] = JSON.stringify(cd11);
}
return fieldsObject;
}
};
return {
setCookie : function(cname, cvalue, exdays) {
methods.setCookie(cname, cvalue, exdays)
},
getCookieValue : function(cname) {
return methods.getCookieValue(cname);
},
calculateScrollPercent: function (absScrollPercent) {
return methods.calculateScrollPercent(absScrollPercent);
},
getScrollText: function (absScrollPercent) {
return methods.getScrollText(absScrollPercent);
},
isIPad: function(fieldsObject) {
return methods.isIPad(fieldsObject);

eventObject.VehCategory.indexOf(CsnInsights.Constants.dealerValues[1]) >= 0) &&
(eventLabel === 'whatsapp_enquiry' || eventLabel === 'whatsapp_share_top')) {

this.trackEnquiry(eventObject, eventContextData);
return;
}
},
getValuesForRange: function (eventData, minKey, maxKey, minValue, maxValue) {
var result = [];
try {
if ((eventData[minKey]) || (eventData[maxKey])) {
if ((eventData[minKey] || '')) { result.push(parseInt(eventData[minKey].toString().replace(/,/g, ''))); }
else { result.push(minValue); }
if ((eventData[maxKey] || '')) { result.push(parseInt(eventData[maxKey].toString().replace(/,/g, ''))); }
else { result.push(maxValue); }
return result;
}
} catch (e) { }
return result;
},
getListingResults: function (sresults) {
var idList = "";
if ((sresults) && typeof (sresults) === 'object') {
var srkeys = Object.keys(sresults);
for (var i = 0; i < srkeys.length; i++) {
sresults[srkeys[i]].forEach(function(listItem) {
idList = idList + (listItem.Id || '').toUpperCase() + ',';
});
}
}
return idList;
},

trackListing: function (eventObject, eventData, searchR) {

if (eventObject['Model']) { eventObject['model'] = eventObject['Model'] }
eventData = eventData || {};
try {
var prange = this.getValuesForRange(eventData, 'pricemin', 'pricemax', 0, 3000000);

eventObject['preferred_price_range'] = prange;
}
} catch (e) { }
try {
if ((eventObject['state_of_vehicle'] || "") === "") {
var stype = (eventData["sellertype"] || "");
var srccond = (eventData["condition"] || "");
if ((stype) && (srccond)) { eventObject['state_of_vehicle'] = stype + '-' + srccond; }
else { eventObject['state_of_vehicle'] = stype + srccond;}
}
} catch (e) { }
try {
var yrange = this.getValuesForRange(eventData, 'yearmin', 'yearmax', 1900, new Date().getFullYear());
if (yrange.length > 0) {
eventObject['year'] = yrange;
} else if (eventData['releaseyear']) {
eventObject['year'] = eventData['releaseyear'];
}
} catch (e) {}
var idlist = this.getListingResults(searchR);
if (idlist) {
eventObject['content_ids'] = idlist;
eventObject['content_type'] = 'vehicle';
}
eventObject['currency'] = eventObject['currency'] || 'CLP';
eventObject['value'] = '0';
var customCampaign = this.getCustomCampaign(eventData);
if ((customCampaign || "") !== "") {
eventObject['search_type'] = customCampaign;
}
else if (eventData['area'] === 'profile-pages') {
eventObject['search_type'] = 'profile_page';
eventObject['content_ids'] = null;
}
fbq('track', 'Search', eventObject);

(function (window) {
var document = window.document;
var screenPercentViewed = 0;
var defaultScreenShown = 0;
var start = Date.now();
if (!window.CsnInsights.EnableScrollTracker)
return;
function ScrollTracker() {
var that = this;
var methods = {
init: function () {
defaultScreenShown = methods.getScreenPercentViewed();
screenPercentViewed = defaultScreenShown;
methods.registerEventListeners();
start = Date.now();
},
registerEventListeners: function () {
window.addEventListener('scroll', methods.scrollListener, true);
},
scrollListener: function (e) {
var scrollPercent = methods.getScreenPercentViewed();
if (typeof (csnInsightsHelper) === 'undefined' ||
typeof (csnInsightsHelper.calculateScrollPercent) !== 'function')
return;
var scrollPercentRange = csnInsightsHelper.calculateScrollPercent(scrollPercent);
if (screenPercentViewed < scrollPercentRange) {
screenPercentViewed = scrollPercentRange;
methods.SendGaEvent('Scroll', scrollPercentRange);
}
},
getScreenPercentViewed: function () {
var screenHeight = Math.min(document.body.clientHeight, document.documentElement.clientHeight);
var scrollPosition = (document.body.scrollTop || document.documentElement['scrollTop']);
var totalHeight = document.documentElement['scrollHeight'];
var percentShown = ((screenHeight + scrollPosition) / totalHeight) * 100;
return percentShown;
},
SendGaEvent: function (eventType, viewPercent) {
if (typeof (CsnInsightsEventTracker) === 'undefined' ||
typeof (CsnInsightsEventTracker.sendEvent) !== 'function' ||
typeof (csnInsightsHelper.calculateScrollPercent) !== 'function' ||
typeof (csnInsightsHelper.getScrollText) !== 'function')
return;
var eventData = {};
eventData["SecondsAfterPageLoad"] = methods.getTimeTakenInSecs();
CsnInsights.metaData["screenviewedonload"] =
csnInsightsHelper.getScrollText(csnInsightsHelper.calculateScrollPercent(defaultScreenShown));
CsnInsightsEventTracker.sendEvent(CsnInsights.metaData, eventType, csnInsightsHelper.getScrollText(viewPercent), eventType,
eventData);
},
getTimeTakenInSecs: function () {
var end = Date.now();
return (end - start) / 1000;
}
};
return {
sendPageView: function (eventContextmetaData, overridePageUrl) {
methods.init();
}
}
}
window.scrollTracker = window.scrollTracker || new ScrollTracker();
window.CsnInsights = window.CsnInsights || {};
if (document.readyState !== 'loading') {
window.scrollTracker.sendPageView();
} else {
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', window.scrollTracker.sendPageView());
}
})(window);
